Azarov Says Japan Will Affect Ukraine Nuclear Policy, FTD Says

-- B y   J e f f   B l a c k
-- 
2011-03-21T07:49:55Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-21/azarov-says-japan-will-affect-ukraine-nuclear-policy-ftd-says.html
Ukrainian Prime Minister  Mykola Azarov  said that his country would draw conclusions from the  Japan  nuclear disaster and rethink its energy strategy,
 Financial Times Deutschland  reported, citing an interview.  Azarov said that Ukraine was pursuing alternative energy
sources, as well as oil- and gas-saving measures, and would
provide tax relief, FTD said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jeff Black in Frankfurt 
